#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:2
#: 4fba85a873ef41d1b5d5a3cc41fdd9d6
msgid "Physics-Informed Learning"
msgstr "物理信息学习"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:4
#: f51974e19b7544f6994e225fa4982aac
msgid ""
"Because every TensorMesh operator is autograd-traced, the assembled FEM "
"system itself can serve as the loss for training a neural network. Rather "
"than *solving* ``K u = F``, we represent the solution by a network "
":math:`u_\\theta(x, y)` and minimise the **discrete Galerkin residual** of "
"the weak form:"
msgstr ""
"由于 TensorMesh 的每个算子都被 autograd 追踪，装配好的 FEM 系统本身就可以充当训练神经网络的损失。我们不是去 *求解* ``K"
" u = F``\\ ，而是用一个网络 :math:`u_\\theta(x, y)` 表示解，并最小化弱形式的 **离散伽辽金残差**\\ ："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:10
#: 24e3f72cc0b541a8a19c36ba5420d506
#, python-brace-format
msgid "\\min_{\\theta}\\;\\; \\big\\| K\\, u_\\theta - F \\big\\|^2 ,"
msgstr "\\min_{\\theta}\\;\\; \\big\\| K\\, u_\\theta - F \\big\\|^2 ,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:14
#: 114cea1caf9447a08e6eaa9a4191e9d7
msgid ""
"where :math:`u_\\theta` is the network evaluated at the mesh nodes. The "
"residual is the FEM (weak-form) residual assembled by TensorMesh — not a "
"strong-form collocation residual — and since ``SparseMatrix.__matmul__`` is "
"differentiable, ``loss = ||K u_theta - F||^2`` back-propagates straight into"
" the network weights. No linear solve, no hand-coded adjoint."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`u_\\theta` 是在网格节点处求值的网络。该残差是由 TensorMesh 装配的 "
"FEM（弱形式）残差——而非强形式配点残差——并且由于 ``SparseMatrix.__matmul__`` 是可微的，\\ ``loss = ||K"
" u_theta - F||^2`` 会直接反向传播到网络权重中。无需线性求解，无需手写伴随。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:20
#: 159b6af8a4514efcb10e8daf779b5123
msgid ""
"This gallery starts with a single Poisson example; the pattern extends to "
"any weak form TensorMesh can assemble."
msgstr "本示例库从单个泊松方程示例开始；该模式可推广到 TensorMesh 能够装配的任意弱形式。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:25
#: 1956166c4de44baaa842a85fbc2492c4
msgid "Poisson via the Galerkin residual — ``poisson_galerkin.py``"
msgstr "通过伽辽金残差求解泊松方程 —— ``poisson_galerkin.py``"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:27
#: 8748277c7f8f4d058552fbb517d35a08
msgid "Solve"
msgstr "求解"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:29
#: 3d7b9104f7dc4a1e9e00250bb1b42378
#, python-brace-format
msgid "-\\Delta u = f \\quad\\text{in }(0,1)^2,\\qquad u = 0 \\text{ on }\\partial\\Omega,"
msgstr "-\\Delta u = f \\quad\\text{in }(0,1)^2,\\qquad u = 0 \\text{ on }\\partial\\Omega,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:33
#: bc55a69070ec4da8ae5bb5347ee2bbd8
msgid ""
"with the manufactured solution :math:`u = \\sin\\pi x\\,\\sin\\pi y` (so "
":math:`f = 2\\pi^2\\,\\sin\\pi x\\,\\sin\\pi y`), which lets us score the "
"network against an analytical field."
msgstr ""
"采用制造解 :math:`u = \\sin\\pi x\\,\\sin\\pi y`\\ （因此 :math:`f = "
"2\\pi^2\\,\\sin\\pi x\\,\\sin\\pi y`\\ ），这使我们能够将网络与解析场进行对照评分。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:37
#: 22a5c72c9390450baa0be4a384221a01
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"TensorMesh assembles the Laplace stiffness :math:`K` and the consistent load"
" :math:`F = M f` **once**; :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` reduces them to "
"the interior system :math:`K_- u = F_-` (homogeneous Dirichlet data). The "
"minimiser of :math:`\\|K_- u - F_-\\|^2` is exactly the FEM solution "
":math:`K_-^{-1}F_-`, so the network is trained to reproduce it:"
msgstr ""
"TensorMesh **一次性**\\ 装配拉普拉斯刚度 :math:`K` 和一致载荷 :math:`F = M f`\\ ；\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` 将它们约化为内部系统 :math:`K_- u = F_-`\\ "
"（齐次狄利克雷数据）。\\ :math:`\\|K_- u - F_-\\|^2` 的最小化解恰好是 FEM 解 "
":math:`K_-^{-1}F_-`\\ ，因此训练网络去复现它："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:76
#: 19487c0b75794f139d35650bcc84d19a
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The squared residual is ill-conditioned (its Hessian is :math:`K_-^{T}K_-`),"
" so — as is standard for physics-informed training — an Adam warm-up is "
"followed by a short **LBFGS** refine, which drives the residual down by "
"another order of magnitude."
msgstr ""
"平方残差是病态的（其海森矩阵为 :math:`K_-^{T}K_-`\\ ），因此——正如物理信息训练中的标准做法——在 Adam 预热之后接一段简短的"
" **LBFGS** 精修，将残差再压低一个数量级。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:85
#: d24de4e83232428aa93bc9038c671cd9
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Training history. Both the relative Galerkin residual and the relative "
":math:`L^2` error against the exact solution fall from "
":math:`\\mathcal{O}(1)`; the periodic spikes are Adam overshooting, and the "
"sharp final drop at iteration 8000 is the LBFGS block."
msgstr ""
"训练历史。相对伽辽金残差与相对于精确解的相对 :math:`L^2` 误差都从 :math:`\\mathcal{O}(1)` 开始下降；周期性的尖峰是"
" Adam 过冲所致，而第 8000 次迭代处那一急剧的最终下降则来自 LBFGS 阶段。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:90
#: 55af6e0c2af64ba6822338c1a246c2cc
msgid "The learned field is indistinguishable from the analytical solution:"
msgstr "学习到的场与解析解难以区分："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:96
#: f98e1d7d48e149f5b0c3e32b61e1907e
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Exact :math:`u` (left), the learned :math:`u_\\theta` (middle), and the "
"absolute error (right, :math:`\\le 6\\times10^{-3}`). The network reaches a "
"relative :math:`L^2` error of about :math:`0.5\\%` against the exact "
"solution and :math:`0.3\\%` against the direct FEM solve — i.e. it recovers "
"the FEM solution to within the mesh's own discretisation error, in about ten"
" seconds on CPU."
msgstr ""
"精确解 :math:`u`\\ （左）、学习到的 :math:`u_\\theta`\\ （中），以及绝对误差（右，\\ :math:`\\le "
"6\\times10^{-3}`\\ ）。网络相对于精确解的相对 :math:`L^2` 误差约为 :math:`0.5\\%`\\ ，相对于直接 "
"FEM 求解的误差约为 :math:`0.3\\%`——也就是说，它在网格自身的离散化误差范围内复现了 FEM 解，在 CPU 上约耗时十秒。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/physics_informed.rst:105
#: 02c05b97f754479da4f2cb32e5a58476
msgid ""
"This is the *variational / Galerkin* flavour of physics-informed learning: "
"the loss is the assembled weak-form residual, so the physics enters exactly "
"as it does in the FEM (one assembly, reused every iteration) and boundary "
"conditions are handled by :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` rather than by a "
"penalty term. The network here is a plain :class:`torch.nn.Module`; see "
":doc:`../user_guide/differentiability` for the three ways to wire a network "
"into a TensorMesh pipeline."
msgstr ""
"这是物理信息学习的 *变分 / 伽辽金* 类型：损失是装配好的弱形式残差，因此物理以与 FEM "
"中完全相同的方式进入（一次装配，每次迭代复用），而边界条件由 :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` "
"处理，而非通过惩罚项。这里的网络是一个普通的 :class:`torch.nn.Module`\\ ；将网络接入 TensorMesh "
"流水线的三种方式参见 :doc:`../user_guide/differentiability`\\ 。"

